<h2 class="bold font-l">Fetch</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Shirou, the wolf-man is easily distracted. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MyInstinctsAreShowing" class='trope-example-link'>My Instincts Are Showing</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
